                <p class="ia-table-text">104.97<authorialNote marker="1"><p class="ia-table-text"> The original IA and RPC Opinion assumed this measure would come into force on 1 October 2017.  The coming into force date is now 6 April 2018.  The IA has been adjusted to show the minor change in impacts – there is a slight change in the net present value (now 104.97 instead of 104.98) and the business net present value (14.78 instead of 14.79).  The RPC Opinion shows a Business Net Present Value of £14.79 million and a Societal Net Present Value of £104.98 million.  The new coming into force date does not change the estimated costs to business.</p></authorialNote></p>
